data.description: WELCOME TO YOUR LAKEFRONT OASIS IN THE AMAZING COMMUNITY OF PORTICO! This modern smart home sits on an oversized lake view lot in one of the best locations in the community (Portico Phase 1)! It features a large, completely fenced-in backyard, making this the perfect home for dog owners! The home boasts 4 spacious bedrooms, 2 beautifully appointed bathrooms and a 3-car garage. Discover elegance and comfort in an Open Living Concept! Great room w/trey ceiling and tall glass sliders, seamlessly connected to the gourmet kitchen w/granite counters, stainless-steel appliances + nice sized breakfast nook. Separate formal dining area, ideal for gatherings with family/friends. Owner suite w/lanai access and ensuite bathroom. Screened-in lanai for cozy outdoor relaxing while relishing gorgeous lake views. NO FLOOD INSURANCE REQUIRED!  Portico is an access-controlled community w/Low HOA fees. Amenities include clubhouse, community pool, gym, yoga/exercise room, tennis, pickleball, basketball, play area. Pets, Fences & LSVs permitted! Great location, short drive to I-75, shopping, dining & more!
